metadata.name: AniNoun 1 (Crocoraffe)
metadata.description:
AniNouns is a collection of breading animals with nouns heads, from father and daughter team ChrisCoCreated and LilTurquoisePanda.

Each AniNoun is a 1 of 1 that comes with breeding capabilities. 

How do I breed:  
Get together with another AniNoun holder and let @LilTurquoiseP know on twitter. You will both have identical twin LilAniNouns airdropped to you, bred from the traits of their parents.

What can I do with my LilAniNoun?  
Grow your LilAniNoun to its mature state (buy buying a grow token), and then breed it with another AniNoun (with a breed token).

We'd love it if you gift your AniNouns to others and grow the fa(r)m.
